&lt;P&gt;I am not a classic server purest, a hardcore player that will be pushing progression, and I am not a PvPer. I just want to restart EQ and be able to progress the the older content without feeling like I am so far behind it is impossible to catch up (I started playing 2004). I made this post not because I really want to change the idea of the progression server but a little tired of all of the different types of players flaming and arguing in the forums about what the server should be (and in my opinion making many wonder if this server is going to be ruined by that fighting). Rather than get involved in the arguments and flaming I figured I would try to offer&amp;nbsp;some type of&amp;nbsp;compromise. Seems more productive than what I see going on in most of the&amp;nbsp;threads I read.&lt;/P&gt;</description>
